title: Cybertroopers Virtual On Soundtracks
description:
Various Virtual On soundtracks. Contains the following albums:
- Beta Tracks
- Counterpoint 009A Episode #16
- CyberNet Rhapsody Episode #14
- Dreamcast Club Trax Sound Data
- Force Official Sould Data Marsinal (Disc 1)
- Force Official Sould Data Marsinal (Disc 2)
- Marz Official Sound Data
- Operation Moongate Official Sound Data
- Oratorio Tangram JP (DreamCast Direct Audio)
- Oratorio Tangram Official Sound Data DNA Side
- Oratorio Tangram Official Sound Data RNA Side
- Oratorio Tangram Remixes

As far as I can tell, this is the full collection of Virtual On related sound material.
